  "dct_description_sm": [
    "United States Major Highways is a polyline theme representing the major highways of the United States. These include interstates, U.S. highways, state highways, and major roads. This dataset is a subset of the Streets dataset. It contains all Class 1 and 2 roads segments plus any other road segments necessary to provide network connectivity for the Class_Rte field."
